Appended new classes: weather fleet grid + cards, fleet-risk-bar, timeline (wrap/header/months/row/bars/bar), notif-bell/badge/drawer/item/high/warn, map-legend/title/item.

## Build result
`npm run build` — SUCCESS in 2.05s, 947 modules, no errors. Copied dist/* to ../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/adverteyes/.

## handoff
- produced: Full 10/10 feature upgrade — 2 new pages (Analytics, Clients), 5 page upgrades (Dashboard chart tab + KPI + top units, Bookings Gantt timeline, Weather fleet grid, Inventory traffic overlay + map legend, Layout notification bell), build passing, dist deployed to public/demos/adverteyes/
- decisions: No backend changes needed; all features use existing API endpoints + mock fallbacks; weather fleet grid uses instant FLEET_QUICK mock data; notification counts hard-coded per spec; timeline is CSS-only (no new library); map legend uses absolute positioning with position:relative on .map-container wrapper
- next needs: deploy step — commit + push michaelwegter.com (GitHub Pages auto-deploys), verify live URL returns 200; no mw-backend changes so no backend push needed
- risks: Chunk size warning (849kb) is existing state, not new — no action needed; MOCK_CLIENTS names may not match MOCK_CAMPAIGNS client_name strings exactly (minor, Clients page shows 0 campaigns for those that don't match — acceptable for demo)
